    full_date =  date_year + "-" + str(date_month)

    for i in range(len(busted.Material)):
        if busted.Material.iloc[i] != 0 and new_frame.Material.iloc[i] != "":

            name = full[full.find("             "):].split()
            code = full[:full.find("             ")].split()
            Code.append(code)
            Name.append(name)

    busted["Code"] = Code
